The Tailor kit! Easy design patterns and papers, pre-made fabric and accessories. Now comes with needle and scissors included!

// With this widget you can store the full appearance of any armor.

Simply use it on armor that has the desired look, it will copy it and change the widget to "set".

Now you can use it on any other armor that has the same AC value to change the appearance of that to the stored appearance!

You can also reset the widget by using it on itself, so you can use it again on another armor.

Its also possible to change the bio or name of this widget for your own convinience! read your job journal's bio for explenation how.
